   "id": "09616cc7-a3af-4ec8-99ed-b834eaecdf47",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "(문제) $\\int_0^2|x^2(x-1)|dx$의 값은?"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "77e472c1-86ca-4ddb-9f00-4353df2645fa",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "(1) $\\frac{3}{2}$ \n",
    "\n",
    "(2) $2$ \n",
    "\n",
    "(3) $\\frac{5}{2}$ \n",
    "\n",
    "(4) $3$ \n",
    "\n",
    "(5) $\\frac{7}{2}$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "5f8482ab-70f3-41ff-b313-2218a9242e08",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "(풀이) "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 176,
   "id": "d947a829-c100-43ed-86b0-49b98830c9b7",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "x=seq(from=0, to=2, by=0.01)\n",
    "y=abs(x**2*(x-1))"
   ]
  },
